# ✨ QR Code Generator

A simple and stylish QR Code Generator built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
Easily generate QR codes from **text, URLs, or any custom input**, and download them with one click.  
Designed with a glowing, responsive UI for a modern look on all devices.  

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🔹 Generate QR codes instantly from:
  - Text
  - Website URLs
  - Any custom string
- 🔹 **Download** QR code as an image
- 🔹 Fully **responsive** design
- 🔹 **Glowing effects** and animations for premium look
- 🔹 Works offline (no external API required)

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML5**
- **CSS3** (Animations, Glowing Effects)
- **JavaScript (qrcode.js)**

🌟 How to Use
Type your text, URL, or any string into the input box.
Click Generate.
Your QR code appears instantly in the center.
Click Download to save it as an image.

📂 Project Structure
qr-generator/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── assets/
│   ├── qrcode.min.js
│   └── background.png

